title: Adobe Muse CC 7.0 [Zeus Downloads]
description:
Adobe Muse CC 7.0
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://www.adobe.com/products/muse.html


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- First make sure you have "Adobe AIR" installed on your mac. If you don't have it installed, then download it from here: http://get.adobe.com/air/ and install it. Don't install Adobe Muse before installing Adobe AIR first.
- Open "Muse_7_0_CCM_LS24.dmg" file. Then open "Adobe Muse" folder > open "payloads" folder > open "AdobeMuse7.0-mul" folder > open "Install Adobe Muse.app".
- Install Adobe Muse CC.
- After Installation is complete, unselect the option to open Adobe Muse.
- Now, copy the "MuseOnAIR.swf" file.
- Go to your Applications folder and find Adobe Muse app.
- Right-Click on "Adobe Muse.app" and click on "Show Package Contents". Open "Contents" folder and then open "Resources" folder.
- Find "MuseOnAIR.swf" file in the "Resources" folder. Delete it and then paste the new "MuseOnAIR.swf" file that you have copied earlier.
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
